# Skill: Content Director

Pilote le pipeline Content Factory (14 etapes, 4 gates). Cree du contenu Instagram via commandes Telegram.

## Quand utiliser ce skill

- Message dans le topic contenu (topic 7)
- Commande /content, /ok, /adjust, /back, /preview, /impact
- Commande gate: /lock-preprod, /lock-script, /ok-rough, /ok-final, /published
- Question sur un contenu en cours de production

## Pipeline: 4 Phases, 14 Etapes

| Phase | Etapes | Gate |
|-------|--------|------|
| I. Pre-production | 1. Brief, 2. Recherche, 3. Moodboard, 4. Concept/Hook, 5. Casting | /lock-preprod |
| II. Ecriture | 6. Script, 7. Storyboard, 8. Sound design | /lock-script |
| III. Production | 9. Generation assets, 10. Rough cut, 11. Fine cut | /ok-rough |
| IV. Post-production | 12. Review final, 13. Multi-format, 14. Publication | /published |

Les etapes auto-enchainables (l'agent les execute sans attendre apres /ok) :
- Etape 2 (Recherche) : search-content skill + web search
- Etape 3 (Moodboard) : generate-visual skill (4-8 images de reference)
- Etape 9 (Generation assets) : delegation a n8n generate-assets workflow
- Etape 10 (Rough cut) : delegation a n8n rough-cut workflow

## APIs Disponibles

### NocoDB via n8n (source de verite)

Toutes les operations CRUD NocoDB passent par n8n webhooks.
Le token NocoDB est stocke dans n8n, pas dans le sandbox agent.

#### Creer un contenu

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/cf-create-content
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
{
  "secret": "${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}",
  "action": "create_content",
  "data": {
    "brand_id": "<brand row id>",
    "title": "<content title>",
    "format": "reel-motion-text|reel-meme-skit|reel-feature-showcase|reel-teaser",
    "brief": { "objective": "...", "target": "...", "message": "...", "constraints": "..." }
  }
}
```

#### Mettre a jour un contenu

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/cf-update-content
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
{
  "secret": "${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}",
  "action": "update_content",
  "content_id": "<id>",
  "data": { "current_step": <N>, "status": "<status>" }
}
```

#### Lire un contenu

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/cf-read-content
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
{
  "secret": "${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}",
  "action": "read_content",
  "content_id": "<id>"
}
```

#### Creer/mettre a jour une scene

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/cf-scene
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
{
  "secret": "${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}",
  "action": "create_scene|update_scene|invalidate_scene|list_scenes",
  "content_id": "<id>",
  "data": { "scene_number": <N>, "description": "...", "status": "..." }
}
```

### Kitsu via n8n (suivi production)

#### Synchroniser avec Kitsu

```
POST {{ n8n_webhook_base_url }}/webhook/cf-kitsu-sync
Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Webhook-Secret: ${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}
Body:
{
  "secret": "${N8N_WEBHOOK_SECRET}",
  "action": "update_task_status|create_shot|upload_preview",
  "content_id": "<id>",
  "data": { "step": <N>, "status": "wip|done|retake|invalidated" }
